namespace MaterialScience.Material.Crystal

    /// <summary>
    /// Definition of space group.
    /// </summary>
    public class SpaceGroup : IComparable<SpaceGroup>
    {
        static readonly SpaceGroup[] groups = new SpaceGroup[530];
        static readonly int[] spacegroupToHallNumber = {

        public int Number { get; private set; }
        public int HallNumber { get; private set; }
        public string SchoenfliesSymbol { get; private set; }
        public string HallSymbol { get; private set; }
        public string Symbol { get; private set; }
        public string LongSymbol { get; private set; }
        public string ShortSymbol { get; private set; }
        public string Setting { get; private set; }
        public CrystalFamily CrystalFamily { get; private set; }
        public CrystalSystem CrystalSystem { get; private set; }
        public LatticeSystem LatticeSystem { get; private set; }
        public LatticeType LatticeType { get; private set; }
        public Centering Centering { get; private set; }
        public PointGroup PointGroup { get; private set; }
        public SpaceGroupOperation[] Operations { get; private set; }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets the space group P1.
        /// </summary>
        public static SpaceGroup P1 => groups[0];


        static SpaceGroup()
        {
            for (int i = 0; i < groups.Length; i++)
                groups[i] = new SpaceGroup();

            groups[0].Number = 1;
            groups[0].HallNumber = 1;
            groups[0].SchoenfliesSymbol = "C1^1";
            groups[0].HallSymbol = "P 1";
            groups[0].Symbol = "P 1";
            groups[0].LongSymbol = "P 1";
            groups[0].ShortSymbol = "P1";
            groups[0].Setting = "";
            groups[0].CrystalFamily = CrystalFamily.Triclinic;
            groups[0].CrystalSystem = CrystalSystem.Triclinic;
            groups[0].LatticeSystem = LatticeSystem.Triclinic;
            groups[0].LatticeType = LatticeType.SimpleTriclinic;
            groups[0].Centering = Centering.Primitive;
            groups[0].PointGroup = PointGroup.FromNumber(1);
            groups[0].Operations = new[] {
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0 }),
            };

                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, -1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 1, 0 }, { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, -1, 0 }, { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, -1, 0 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, 1, 0 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, 1, 0 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, -1, 0 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, -1, 0 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, 1, 0 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, 1, 0 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, -1, 0 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, -1, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, -1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 1, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, -1, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, 1, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { -1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 0, -1, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 1, 0, 0 } }, new[] { 6 / 12.0, 6 / 12.0, 0 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { 1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, -1 }, { 0, 1, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
                new SpaceGroupOperation(new double[,] { { -1, 0, 0 }, { 0, 0, 1 }, { 0, -1, 0 } }, new[] { 3 / 12.0, 3 / 12.0, 9 / 12.0 }),
            };
        }


        /// <summary>
        /// Gets space group by space group number.
        /// </summary>
        public static SpaceGroup FromNumber(int n)
        {
            if (n <= 0 || n > 230)
                throw new Exception("Invalid space group number.");
            return groups[spacegroupToHallNumber[n - 1] - 1];
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets space group by Hall space group number.
        /// </summary>
        public static SpaceGroup FromHallNumber(int n)
        {
            if (n <= 0 || n > 530)
                throw new Exception("Invalid Hall space group number.");
            return groups[n - 1];
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets space group by symmetry operations.
        /// </summary>
        public static SpaceGroup FromOperations(SpaceGroupOperation[] operations)
        {
            foreach (var g in groups)
                if (Compare(g.Operations, operations))
                    return g;
            throw new Exception("Invalid space group symmetry operations");
        }

        public static bool Compare(SpaceGroupOperation[] ops1, SpaceGroupOperation[] ops2)
        {
            if (ops1.Length != ops2.Length) return false;
            var visit = new bool[ops2.Length];
            foreach (var op1 in ops1)
            {
                for (int i = 0; i < ops2.Length; i++)
                    if (visit[i] == false && op1 == ops2[i]) { visit[i] = true; goto next; }
                return false;
                next: continue;
            }
            return true;
        }



        /// <summary>
        /// Gets all sites by applying symmetry operations.
        /// </summary>
        public Site[] GetSites(Site[] reduced_sites, bool primitive_cell)
        {
            if (this == P1)
                return reduced_sites;

            var sites = new List<Site>();
            if (primitive_cell)
            {
                var T = Lattice.GetCMatrixToStandard(Centering);        // T x = x'
                var T_inv = Lattice.GetCMatrixToPrimitive(Centering);
                foreach (var site in reduced_sites)
                {
                    var p0 = T_inv * site.Position;     // position in standard cell
                    var images = new List<Site>();
                    foreach (var op in Operations)
                    {
                        var p = T * op.Apply(p0);     // position in primitive cell
                        foreach (var image in images)
                            if (image.At(p))
                                goto next;
                        images.Add(new Site(site, p));
                        next: continue;
                    }
                    sites.AddRange(images);
                }
            }
            else
            {
                foreach (var site in reduced_sites)
                {
                    var p0 = site.Position;
                    var images = new List<Site>();
                    foreach (var op in Operations)
                    {
                        var p = op.Apply(p0);
                        foreach (var image in images)
                            if (image.At(p))
                                goto next;
                        images.Add(new Site(site, p));
                        next: continue;
                    }
                    sites.AddRange(images);
                }
            }
            return sites.ToArray();
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets reduced sites by applying symmetry operations.
        /// </summary>
        public Site[] GetReducedSites(Site[] sites, bool primitive_cell)
        {
            if (this == P1)
                return sites;

            // T x = x'
            var T = Matrix.Identity(3);
            var T_inv = Matrix.Identity(3);
            if (primitive_cell)
            {
                T = Lattice.GetCMatrixToStandard(Centering);
                T_inv = Lattice.GetCMatrixToPrimitive(Centering);
            }

            var reduced_sites = new List<Site>();
            for (var i = 0; i < sites.Length; i++)
            {
                if (sites[i] == null) continue;
                var p0 = T_inv * sites[i].Position;     // position in standard cell
                var delta = new Vector(0, 0, 0);
                var nImages = 1;
                foreach (var op in Operations)
                {
                    var p = T * op.Apply(p0);     // position in primitive cell
                    for (var j = i + 1; j < sites.Length; j++)
                        if (sites[j] != null && sites[j].EquivalentTo(sites[i]) && sites[j].At(p))
                        {
                            delta += Vector.RoundDistance(sites[j].Position, p);
                            nImages++;
                            sites[j] = null;
                        }
                }
                reduced_sites.Add(new Site(sites[i], p0 + delta / nImages));
            }
            return reduced_sites.ToArray();
        }


        public int CompareTo(SpaceGroup other) => Number.CompareTo(other.Number);

        public static implicit operator SpaceGroup(int number) => FromNumber(number);

        public override string ToString()
        {
            return $"{ShortSymbol} ({Number})";
        }
    }

    public static class SpaceGroupFinder
    {
        

        // <summary>
        // Finds the space group.
        // </summary>
        public static CrystalStructure FindSpaceGroup(this CrystalStructure structure, double tolerance = 0.01)
            => FindSpaceGroup(structure.Lattice, structure.Sites, tolerance);

        //public static SpaceGroup SpaceGroupSymbol(Lattice lattice, Site[] sites, double tolerance = 0.01)
        //{

        //}

        public static CrystalStructure FindSpaceGroup(Lattice lattice, Site[] sites, double tolerance = 0.01)
        {
            var positions = new double[sites.Length, 3];
            for (var i = 0; i < sites.Length; i++)
            {
                positions[i, 0] = sites[i].X;
                positions[i, 1] = sites[i].Y;
                positions[i, 2] = sites[i].Z;
            }

            var types = new int[sites.Length];
            for (var i = 0; i < sites.Length; i++)
            {
                types[i] = i;
                for (var j = 0; j < i; j++)
                    if (sites[i].EquivalentTo(sites[j]))
                    {
                        types[i] = j;
                        break;
                    }
            }

            //int n_std_sites = 0;
            //var stdLattice = new double[3, 3];
            //var stdPositions = new double[sites.Length * 4, 3];
            //var stdTypes = new int[sites.Length * 4];
            // var number = spg_get_spacegroup(lattice.Matrix.Transpose().Data, positions, types, sites.Length, tolerance, ref n_std_sites, stdLattice, stdPositions, stdTypes);

            var symbol = new char[21];
            var number = Spglib.spg_get_international(symbol, lattice.Matrix.Transpose().Data, positions, types, sites.Length, tolerance);
            

            SpaceGroup sg = SpaceGroup.FromNumber(number);

            return CrystalStructure.FromSites(lattice, sg, sites);
        }
    }
}
